The Examen doesnot require the candidate to set up a envirnoment, 
The course needs to do much pratice to feel confident as the exam is a full handson exercices, 
  be confident with YAML 
  be confident with Vim 

Must know for CKAD exam: 
This exam is for the application developers who need to know how to design, to build and confugure cloud native application.  

  - Core concepts 
  - Multi-Container pods
  - Logging and monitoring 
  - Jobs
  - Demos 
  - ConfigMaps, Secrets, ....
  - Readiness and liveness probes
  - Services

During the exam, candidates have acces to the kubernets documentation 

Certified Kubernetes Application Developer: https://www.cncf.io/certification/ckad/

Candidate Handbook: https://www.cncf.io/certification/candidate-handbook

Exam Tips: https://docs.linuxfoundation.org/tc-docs/certification/tips-cka-and-ckad

